    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> with your<strong> ground turmeric</strong>, a small splash of <strong>cold water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>in a small bowl – this is your <strong>turmeric yoghurt</strong></p>",
